  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK229">
<l>irattali ṉiṉṉātu maṉṟa nirappiya</l>
<l>tāmē tamiya ruṇal</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Solitary and unshared eating for the sake of filling up one's own riches is certainly much more unpleasant than begging.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
